1/10/2002

-- gg - db.c: renum_zone_table(): Better explanation of what it does, also
		noting some assumptions it makes.  Fixed to use room_rnum
		instead of just 'int'.

-- gg - utils.c: room_is_dark(): New, from the old IS_DARK() macro.
