1/27/2002

-- gg - act.other.c, act.wizard.c, ban.c, class.c, comm.c, db.c, fight.c,
		house.c, interpreter.c, limits.c, modify.c, objsave.c,
		spells.c, utils.c, utils.h: Variable argument mudlog().

